# Storyboard Output Format — Piloc Motion Agent

This template defines the exact structure of a Phase 2 storyboard.
Read this file before drafting any storyboard. Do not deviate from this format.

---

## Template

```
## STORYBOARD: [Feature] — [Platform] [Duration]
Total Length: [Xs] | Total Frames: [N] @ 30fps | Scenes: [#]
Dimensions: [W×H] | Platform: [LinkedIn 16:9 / LinkedIn 16:9 + Square / YouTube]
Music: [track name + BPM, or "none"]
UI Source: [HTML prototype / Screenshots / Both]

---

### SCENE [N]: [SCENE NAME]
Frames: [sceneIn]–[sceneOut] ([Xs])
SceneHeadline: chip=[PILOC · FEATURE] | title=[white part] | accent=[mist part]

Story beat: [what this scene communicates — one sentence]
UI elements shown: [list of 2–5 components, e.g. "KPI strip (3 cards), table (5 rows)"]
Key animation event: [the one thing that happens, e.g. "badge flips VALIDÉ at frame 268"]

Remotion Animation Notes:
  - Entry: [fade + slide description, start frame]
  - Key events: [frame → what changes]
  - Exit: [fdOut description, end frame]

---

### DRAFT TIMELINE (const TL)
[Sketch of scene boundaries — exact values computed in Phase 3.5 Section A]
heroIn: 0
heroOut: ~80
dashIn: ~90
...
ctaIn: ~[N]
totalDur: ~[N] ([Xs])

---

### ASSET CHECKLIST
- [ ] SVG icon paths: [list from HTML symbols]
- [ ] Data values: [real values extracted from HTML/screenshots]
- [ ] Music: [in/music/track.mp3 — confirmed present / not needed]
- [ ] Voiceover: [yes/no — to confirm in Phase 3]
```

---

## Architecture rules (always apply)

- **Single file per video:** `remotion/src/videos/[Feature]Demo.tsx` — self-contained, no sub-files.
- **Frame-based architecture:** multiple `AbsoluteFill` scenes, each fades in/out by TL. Each scene returns `null` outside its window. See `references/patterns` #12.
- **No TextOverlay component.** The SceneHeadline title IS the narrative for muted viewers.
- **No `@remotion/google-fonts`.** Use `waitForInter()` from `./fonts`.
- **No multi-file structure** (no `Root.tsx`, no `compositions/`, no `scenes/`, no `ui/`).
- **Background:** `#0E1029` flat, no SVG, no gradient.
- **Registration:** after writing the file, add it to `src/index.tsx` with `id` = filename without `.tsx`.

