## Worked Example: Campagnes — LinkedIn 30s

```
## STORYBOARD: Campagnes — LinkedIn 16:9 + Square 30s
Total Length: 30s | Total Frames: 900 @ 30fps | Scenes: 4
Dimensions: 1920×1080 (+ 1080×1080 square) | Platform: LinkedIn
Music: none
UI Source: HTML prototype + screenshots

---

### SCENE 1: HERO
Frames: 0–80 (2.7s)
SceneHeadline: chip=PILOC · CAMPAGNES | title=Relancez vos impayés | accent=sans effort

Story beat: Brand entry — establish product identity, hook the viewer before any UI.
UI elements shown: PilocLogo + chip + two-line kinetic title
Key animation event: Logo spring-in at frame 0, title lines slide up staggered at +14/+24.

Remotion Animation Notes:
  - Logo: spring scale 0.7→1, damping:18 stiffness:120, frame 0
  - Chip: fade+translateY, frame 12
  - Line 1: translateY(18→0) + opacity, frame 20
  - Line 2: translateY(18→0) + opacity, frame 30
  - Exit: fdOut all elements at heroOut-16

---

### SCENE 2: DASHBOARD
Frames: 90–310 (7.3s)
SceneHeadline: chip=PILOC · CAMPAGNES | title=Visualisez vos relances | accent=en un coup d'œil

Story beat: Beat 1 — dashboard loads, operator sees the full state of their campaigns at a glance.
UI elements shown: KPI strip (3 cards: Taux de recouvrement, Montant relancé, Campagnes actives), campaign table (5 rows)
Key animation event: KPIs count up simultaneously at frame 106. Table appears at 126, all rows fade in together.

Remotion Animation Notes:
  - Scene fade: opacity 0→1, frames 90–106
  - KPIs: simultaneous, spring opacity frame 106, count up 106→190
  - Table card: fade+translateY(10→0), frame 126
  - Rows: simultaneous opacity 0→1, frames 138–154 (Beat 1 initial load)
  - Badges + progress bars: stagger 6f/row starting frame 154
  - Exit: fdOut at dashOut-20

---

### SCENE 3: CAMPAGNE DETAIL
Frames: 320–620 (10s)
SceneHeadline: chip=PILOC · CAMPAGNES | title=Choisissez le bon canal | accent=par segment

Story beat: Beat 2 — operator selects a campaign and configures the send channel.
UI elements shown: Campaign detail card (name, status, canal selector as grid cards)
Key animation event: Canal grid cards stagger in at frame 380. Selection spring-pops at frame 450.

Remotion Animation Notes:
  - Detail card: spring translateY(20→0) + opacity, frame 320
  - Canal cards (×3): stagger 10f, spring scale 0→1, frames 380/390/400
  - Selected card: spring scale 1→1.05→1 (spring pop) at frame 450
  - Confirmation badge: fade+scale, frame 490
  - Exit: fdOut at scene3Out-20

---

### SCENE 4: CTA
Frames: 630–900 (9s)
SceneHeadline: (none — Hero-loop format)

Story beat: Beat 4 — brand close, invite to act.
UI elements shown: PilocLogo + chip PILOC · CAMPAGNES + two-line kinetic title
Key animation event: Logo spring-in at ctaIn, chip +12, line1 +20, line2 +30. Hold ≥3s.

Remotion Animation Notes:
  - Logo: spring scale 0.7→1, damping:18 stiffness:120
  - Chip: fade+translateY, ctaIn+12
  - Line 1 (white): translateY(18→0), ctaIn+20
  - Line 2 (mist accent): translateY(18→0), ctaIn+30
  - No exit — holds to end

